Gen Info - Questions about general information about credit card. For ex:- What is credit card?, How to apply for card? etc.
Interest & Apr - Questions about credit card interest rate.
Queries - General Questions inquiring about working and various technical terms regarding credit card.
Rewards - Questions about rewards and cashback offers of various banks.
Bills,Statement and limit - Questions about credit card's bill , statement , transactions, balance, etc. and credit limit.
PIN -  questions regarding PIN of credit cards.
Contactless - Questions about contactless payments 
Score report - Questions about credit score and report.
Online- Inquiries about online transactions and internet banking.
Bank & customer care - Banks specific questions.
Charges & fees - questions about various charges levied on the card.
Debt -  About credit debt
Fraud,Loss,Theft & Disputes - Questions about fraudulent activities and disputes against banks.
